  title VARCHAR(255),
  editor VARCHAR(100),
  published_date DATE,
  volume INT
)

CREATE TABLE publications (
  publication_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  title VARCHAR(255),
  publisher VARCHAR(100),
  published_date DATE
)

### STATEMENT

SELECT * FROM books WHERE author IN ('Stephanie Meyer', 'Suzanne Collins');
